title: [Northern Slopes, Arctic Track]
description: The snow is crusted into a brittle carapace with ice, marred here and there with stone outcrops that shine with a frozen veneer.  To the wind's sighs and murmurs is added the occasional cry of an eagle flying high above, adding an eerie chord to the winter lullaby and echoing like a siren's call across the ocean waves.

The snow is crusted into a brittle carapace with ice, marred here and there with stone outcrops that shine with a frozen veneer.  To the wind's sighs and murmurs is added the occasional cry of a snowy owl high above, adding an eerie chord to the winter lullaby and echoing like a siren's call across the ocean waves.
